First Web API Tutorial Mod
--------------------------
original path:
https://github.com/dotnet/AspNetCore.Docs/tree/main/aspnetcore/tutorials/first-web-api

Local copies and modification:
/first-web-api

extended the code for the purpose of creating a kubernetes training example based on the application
- refactored data context code into a second project, TodoService ( in progress )
- to communicate with additional service(s)  ( in progress )
- added dockerfile(s)
- implementation and config changes for containerised microservice support ( in progress )
- added kubernetes deployment config ( in progress )
